name: Oh-Peak, It's Osmeña Peak!
description: Osmeña Peak is considered to be the rugged hills in Cebu, which is exactly located in Mantalongon, Dalaguete, Cebu. Mantalongon is considered as the "Summer Capital in Cebu". So when you go there you can feel the very cool atmosphere of the place. If you are adventurous and brave enough to climb it's peak you'll see a very beautiful view from it's peak.
